<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application>gmp</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>gmp</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=/usr --infodir=/usr/share/info --mandir=/usr/share/man &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

